nodes.text: The Caravel was the personal starship of Mungo Baobab. As part of the Baobab Merchant Fleet, the vessel had also been used by the Mungo's prestigious ancestor, Ebenn Q3 Baobab. Following Mungo's capture in The Cloak of the Sith, Caravel was briefly captured by Roon's Governor Koong before eventually being returned to its owner.
